version_description: This is kind of 3 tabs in 1 song,i have included intro and verse 1 which use clean electric guitar,then 1st instrumental into verse 2 using distortion/compression guitar ,then into verse 3 which uses accoustic guitar/clean electric.Using the maj7 s and m6 sounds good and no capo is required.On the link it is easier to do A5, D5 , C5,but its not as accurate.
